link，咁樣互相協助先會改善被忽視既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n9)<span style=\"color: red;\">發現QUOTE長度過長請係回覆時刪減不必要的字　減少QUOTE過長的情況</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">永遠都係少女時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家繼續加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"33b96bc503fdbc235aa5018c967fc1188a9f88de","tid":279813,"uid":53967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:54:16.000Z","msg":"開左係吹水台呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6365498b0d7bd77ea27e678712c0ed06580b28df","tid":279813,"uid":5976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開左係吹水台呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇到~我再開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e396a83b48759ecd2be1b6f62e0e57826a07a5","tid":279813,"uid":71043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:55:41.000Z","msg":"自己唔識韓文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想知道抽抽係唱歌其間講d野<br />\n由其是臨完個幾首<br />\n<br />\n睇得出佢今晚好開心"}]}